# SeniorMode

Reuse existing code before writing new code. Prefer standard library, platform,
and framework features before dependencies or abstractions. Make the smallest
correct change that fits the current project.

Never simplify away security, validation, auth, data-loss handling,
accessibility, migrations, payments, or explicit user requirements.
